These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, pear
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, subway
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the subway is not the person eating pear##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | pear   | nectarine  |
| Sport   | jet-ski | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
2 different games are played: go, whist
2 different pets are kept: goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the goat is not the person playing whist##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | go | whist      |
| Pet    | goat  | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
There 2 different types of food: plum, pumpkin
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, lilac
1. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person eating plum##1
2. the person who likes blue is not the person eating plum##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | pumpkin  | plum    |
| Sport   | blue | lilac |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
House: colonial, palace
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster
1. the palace house is not the owner of the goldfish##6
2. the palace house is somewhere to the right of the colonial house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2      |
| Food   | colonial  | palace |
| Pet    | goldfish | hamster    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-5::.
2 different games are played: snooker, canasta
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, lacrosse
1. the person playing canasta is not the person who's sport is lacrosse##6
2. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | snooker  | canasta |
| Sport         | lacrosse | golf      |

